{"tid":2183460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"捷克參議院議長立法院演講 以中文「我是台灣人」作結","createTime":"2020-09-01T03:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T03:39:57.000Z","uid":2054,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f369a7776875af77e084637303007897c19d07ae","tid":2183460,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:00:24.000Z","msg":"蘋果全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200901/MITJHIH4HBBANP3ZGX7HQYCRO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200901%2FMITJHIH4HBBANP3ZGX7HQYCRO4%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7vTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=2b963da5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200901%2FMITJHIH4HBBANP3ZGX7HQYCRO4%2F&h=4cb8bf0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200901/MITJHIH4HBBANP3ZGX7HQYCRO4/</a><br />\n<br />\n（更新內容）捷克參議院議長維特齊（Milo&scaron; Vystrčil）今日（9月1日）進入第3三日訪台行程，早上會拜訪立法院，並演講約45分鐘。維特齊在演講中再次談及民主價值，並在演講的最後，以中文「我是台灣人」作結，全場起立鼓掌發言讓全場起立鼓掌。立法院長游錫堃除致詞歡迎，同時代表立法院致贈紀念議事槌、立法院國會外交榮譽一等獎章給維特齊。但游錫堃在頒贈獎章給維特齊時，還一度戴反，最後在議事人員協助下順利配戴。<br />\n<br />\n維特齊表示，捷克與台灣很相似，都為了追求民主自由而努力。他倡議民主國家應團結，捍衞共同價值，而他有機會在台灣最高的立法機關發言，感到十分榮幸。"},{"pid":"cc673712b542c20b2f61806e3b8c7fef8a3fa33f","tid":2183460,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:08:06.000Z","msg":"我係台灣人啊hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61823b5dfac3cb8bd2052628416561a4d2336ce","tid":2183460,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:13:57.000Z","msg":"佢都無居留權"},{"pid":"9fae6b3bff3611ee720b6f80f3edcd67893dce58","tid":2183460,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36867e71305c47bd72d9d967be4f8aaccce0d597","tid":2183460,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:27:13.00